    {
      "id": "jsc-md-1",
      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "# D3.js Data Science Visualizations\n\nAll 8 essential chart types for data science — rendered **inline as SVG** using D3.js.\nEach cell is fully self-contained. Run any cell individually or **Run All** from top to bottom.\n\n| Cell | Chart Type | Use Case |\n|------|-----------|----------|\n| 2 | Bar Chart | Categorical comparison |\n| 3 | Line Chart | Time series / trends |\n| 4 | Scatter Plot | Correlation + regression |\n| 5 | Histogram | Frequency distribution |\n| 6 | Donut Chart | Proportional breakdown |\n| 7 | Heatmap | Correlation matrix |\n| 8 | Box Plot | Statistical comparison |\n| 9 | Area Chart | Cumulative / multi-channel |\n\n## Prerequisites\nInstall `d3` in **Packages → npm** tab (one click).",
      "output": "",
      "returnValue": null,
      "executed": false,
